ACKNOWLEDGMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project uses data from the following sources:

1. NOAA Global Monitoring Laboratory - Keeling Curve
   https://gml.noaa.gov/ccgg/trends/
   Data used under NOAA data use policy

2. SOCAT (Surface Ocean CO₂ Atlas)
   https://www.socat.info/
   SOCAT is an international collaborative project

3. GLODAP (Global Ocean Data Analysis Project)
   https://www.glodap.info/
   GLODAP is a product of the Global Ocean Observing System

4. NASA Earth Observing System
   - MODIS (Moderate Resolution Imaging Spectroradiometer)
   - OCO-2 (Orbiting Carbon Observatory-2)
   Data available through NASA Earthdata

5. GTN-P (Global Terrestrial Network for Permafrost)
   https://gtnp.arcticportal.org/
   Supported by the International Permafrost Association

6. Global Carbon Project
   https://www.globalcarbonproject.org/
   Future Earth research project

7. FLUXNET
   https://fluxnet.org/
   Global network of eddy covariance towers

8. ECMWF ERA5 Reanalysis
   https://www.ecmwf.int/en/forecasts/datasets/reanalysis-datasets/era5
   Copernicus Climate Change Service

